{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#4874: reactivity does not work on root component props when using createApp",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:27:05.469613+00:00",
  "text": "reactivity does not work on root component props when using createApp\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.20\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[sfc.vuejs.org/](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nPass a `reactive({})` object into `createApp`'s second parameter, update a property on it.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nThe root component should update.\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nThe root component is not updating.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "has workaround",
    ":cake: p2-nice-to-have"
  ],
